* Use of select command to display a menu of names

PS3='select names : '
names='pavan harsha abid quit'
select name in $names
do
if [ $name == 'quit' ]
then
break
fi
echo hello $name
done

OUTPUT

1) pavan
2) harsha
3) abid
4) quit
select names : 1
hello pavan
select names : 2
hello harsha
select names : 3
hello abid
select names : 4
